		<h2 class="heading-2 awards__title mb-lg">Awards</h2>
		<h3 class="heading-3 awards__heading--1">Brit Awards</h3>
      	<ul class="awards__list">
			<li><strong>1977</strong> - British Single of the Year (Bohemian Rhapsody)</li>
			<li><strong>1990</strong> - Outstanding Contribution To Music (Queen)</li>	
			<li><strong>1992</strong> - British Single of the Year (These Are The Days Of Our Life)</li>	
